{"tid":1480642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當抗爭變成習慣......","createTime":"2019-08-17T11:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T10:28:16.000Z","uid":61161,"like":16,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6f3f4a68cde12444ffbdd61a54a5a83923d8fa","tid":1480642,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:38:58.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，大部份香港人都喺善忙嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果林鄭個on9特首一早講撤回，又點會發到件事咁大丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家抗爭已經變成習慣，大大增長港共政權嘅管治成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住落黎只有兩個結局：（無第三個）<br />\n1. 中共跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#香港人加油<br />\n#無得再輸<br />\n#一輸就會輸多十年<br />\n#林鄭讓抗爭變成習慣"},{"pid":"2f04c19fadfbf1d53e403e01f3712ba30c084934","tid":1480642,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"993e3a25aceb1d95a10e4a6030ff31fdd6dbfccb","tid":1480642,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"701e8ba7cab9e5e13001c56a025e05e1ce8f95bf","tid":1480642,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:41:38.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"3f5055f75b55c2e22e8137f38685ba8118a1d780","tid":1480642,"uid":91721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"睇多兩個月先好講習慣"},{"pid":"b9bc9ef6a198720c6f675d4c88c17bdaaa7f144a","tid":1480642,"uid":162330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"仲未可以習慣到冇感覺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好攰一坐低就瞓着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔堅持就可以等去集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf795a605